  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World War 3 is a card game where you can play as all your favorite countries and their world leaders:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>USA<br></li><li>France<br></li><li>UK<br></li><li>Germany<br></li><li>North Korea</li></ul><br><br><br><br>The cards show real & historical flavor text, quoted from the history books.  <br>You will be able to cast spells, heal, use direct damage, and use short or long-range attacks.<br><br>Formulate a strategy against your opponents using your deck, whoever has the highest score wins!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3 levels of difficulty:</h2>Easy, Medium, and Get Wrecked<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We plan to implement online multiplayer support, but it is not officially confirmed at the current time.</h2><br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World War 3 is a card game where you can play as all your favorite countries and their world leaders:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>USA<br></li><li>France<br></li><li>UK<br></li><li>Germany<br></li><li>North Korea</li></ul><br><br><br><br>The cards show real & historical flavor text, quoted from the history books.  <br>You will be able to cast spells, heal, use direct damage, and use short or long-range attacks.<br><br>Formulate a strategy against your opponents using your deck, whoever has the highest score wins!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3 levels of difficulty:</h2>Easy, Medium, and Get Wrecked<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We plan to implement online multiplayer support, but it is not officially confirmed at the current time.</h2><br><br>",
